'''拉加'''（Raga）是[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]西北部的小鎮，由[[西加扎勒河州|西加扎勒河州]]負責管轄，毗鄰與[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]和[[中非共和國|中非共和國]]接壤的邊界，位於首都[[朱巴|朱巴]]西北約950公里<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)%20&toplace=Raga%20(Bahr%20al%20Ghazal%20Wilayat)%20&fromlat=4.872006&tolat=8.4666667&fromlng=31.601117&tolng=25.6833333 |title=Esstimated Road Distance Between Juba And Raga With Map |accessdate=2011-09-12 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202818/http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)%20&toplace=Raga%20(Bahr%20al%20Ghazal%20Wilayat)%20&fromlat=4.872006&tolat=8.4666667&fromlng=31.601117&tolng=25.6833333 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，平均海拔高度545米<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wunderground.com/global/stations/62871.html |title=Raga's Elevation Is 1,788 Feet Above Sea Level |access-date=2011-09-12 |archive-date=2016-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916095416/https://www.wunderground.com/global/stations/62871.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，鎮上有機場設施，2010年人口3,700<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.geonames.org/search.html?q=raga&country=SD |title=Estimated Population In 2010 |access-date=2011-09-12 |archive-date=2019-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924125225/http://www.geonames.org/search.html?q=raga&country=SD |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

